                    "Baggage fees for one checked bag each way are reimbursable on all trips; a second checked bag is reimbursable only when the trip requires equipment, marketing materials, or client deliverables that would not otherwise fit, and the expense report should note the business reason. Airport parking or long-term parking at the traveler's home airport is reimbursable up to the cost of a reasonable round-trip rideshare fare to the same airport, whichever is lower.",
