                    "Approved reimbursements to a personal payment method are processed on Contoso Corp's standard accounts payable cycle, which runs weekly, and funds are typically deposited within 10 business days of final approval. Employees paid through payroll-linked reimbursement, where permitted by local payroll rules described in the Contoso Corp Compensation and Pay Practices Policy, may instead see approved reimbursements appear on their next regular pay cycle.",
